## Intentionally inert. Power-up pickups are placed by hand in the map, not auto-spawned.
##
## This file only exists because the Godot editor keeps restoring a "PowerUpSpawner" autoload
## entry in project.godot from its in-memory project settings; without the file the autoload
## fails to load and spams errors. To remove it for good: Project > Project Settings >
## Autoload, delete "PowerUpSpawner", then this file can be deleted too.
